{"tid":475522,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"浪客劍心北海道篇 宣佈完結","createTime":"2017-11-21T07:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T17:16:25.000Z","uid":34409,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e76f586640b4efc32a5199c173285d219646c3d5","tid":475522,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"人氣漫畫《浪客劍心》作者和月伸宏，因為持有幼女裸體影片，21日被日本警視廳以違反兒童買春・兒童情色禁止法函送法辦。<br />\n<br />\n據《讀賣新聞》報導，本名西脇伸宏的漫畫家和月伸宏，今年10月被警方發現事務所內，有多片10多歲幼女裸體DVD影片，西脇伸宏坦承持有「喜歡國小高年級到國中2年級的女童」。警方會發現西脇伸宏持有幼女裸體DVD，是因為在調查其他兒童情色事件時，查到西脇伸宏有購買，於是前往他住處進行搜查。<br />\n<br />\n日本兒童情色法，如果持有性相關、未滿18歲兒童的物品，將處1年以下徒刑，或100萬日圓(約27萬新台幣)以下罰金。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171121/1245195/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171121%2F1245195%2F&d=mg95djlf9FHQSCc7LfRtz4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9b2b07f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171121%2F1245195%2F&h=31119d20\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171121/1245195/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電影版可以慳返唔駛拍第三集了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fb0d5d499de2feceef59d77e9645e7c59b5e57","tid":475522,"uid":124868,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"係監倉繼續畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13826fb0f65ea7ab5efe99be2fdf3db6d1709b59","tid":475522,"uid":40226,"like":6,"dislike":16,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T07:59:58.000Z","msg":"其實浪客劍心一啲都唔好睇<br />\n一諗起個on9女主就唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f5e5da55cc71cb29547176bf90823a1b0d394d","tid":475522,"uid":51665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實浪客劍心一啲都唔好睇<br />\n一諗起個on9女主就唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/